    "heading": "Undo with the inverse",
    "intro": "<p>Multiplication and division are <strong>inverses</strong> — they undo each other. <strong>3x</strong> means 3 times x. To find x, divide by 3. Then <strong>substitute</strong> back to check.</p>",
